<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Dieter II. Landschad von Steinach, Viztum zu Aschaffenburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass die Juden David und Seligman Pützel trotz mehrfacher Verlängerungen ihres Geleits den rechtzeitigen Austrag der Streitsache ihres Bruders Josef vor dem Reichsgericht zu Nürnberg versäumt und sich in der Stadt unziemlich verhalten haben, aber verlängert ihr Geleit dem Adressaten und Erzbischof Konrad III. von Mainz zuliebe bis Katharinentag und hofft auf fristgerechten Austrag.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_183" id="90v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_183_r1l12"><expan>Dıeth<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lantſchad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Aſchaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_183_r1l13"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Yoſep pücʒels <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l14">vnd ſeinr <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu wırdt dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l15">ſache <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> niht recht fürbracht vnd <expan>ſuche<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe Juden vns <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l16">eẅch ʒu <expan>u<ex>er</ex>unglımpfe<ex>n</ex></expan> / des wır eẅch doch niht <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu gelawben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l17">wan nach dem wır <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Yoſeps <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l18">ʒu dıenſt vnd von <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> bett <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ſo langeʒeıt <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> geleyt bey vns <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l19">vnd erlengt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / ſo <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> ſıe ſein ſacheılt vnd ſach gen den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l20">nach des Reıchs gerıchts form bey vns in <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒeıt pıllıch vnd wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l21">ein bracht vnd <expan>auſʒgetrag<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe gewölt daʒ dıe ſeẅmnuſſ Jr <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l22">ıſt als wır <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> / Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſıch der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Yoſep Jud vnd ſein <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l23">bey vns alſo <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wır ſıe <expan>lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>ſwo</expan> ſehen denn bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l24">VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meıncʒ <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l25">lıeb / <expan>VVell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır des <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Yoſeps <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> geleyt bey vns <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l26"><expan>erleng<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> ſand kathreyn tag ſchıerıſt . Vnd <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅch wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l27">Jr beſtellet mıt Jn daʒ ſıe ır ſache in <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒeıt . <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> auſʒtrag bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l28"><expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> bett in der ſache vnd <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Juden bey vns . für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_183_r1l29">bas <expan>v̈berhabe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_183" id="90v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Dieth<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lantschad<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Aschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan>, als ir uns aber
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, von Yosep Püczels
                                <expan>jude<ex>n</ex></expan> und seinr
                            <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu wirdt die sache
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> niht recht fürbracht und
                                <expan>suche<ex>n</ex></expan> die juden uns
                            <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>unglimpfe<ex>n</ex></expan>, des wir ewch doch
                        niht <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> zu gelawben, wan nach dem wir
                                <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> Yoseps
                            <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz zu dienst und von
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> bett <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> so
                        langezeit <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> geleyt bey uns
                            <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> und erlengt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        so <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> sie sein sacheilt und sach gen den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nach des reichs gerichts form bey uns
                        in <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit pillich und wol ein bracht und
                                <expan>auszgetrag<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sie gewölt, daz die sewmnuss ir <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, als wir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>. Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sich der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Yosep jud und sein
                                <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns also
                            <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir sie
                            <expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>swo</expan> sehen, denn bey uns. Wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu lieb, <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir des <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Yoseps
                            <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> geleyt bey uns <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>erleng<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">sand Kathreyn tag schierist</q>21.11.1420</note>
</app>; und <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> ewch wol, ir bestellet mit in,
                        daz sie ir sache in <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit
                                <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> ausztrag bey uns
                                <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> bett in der sache und
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> juden bey uns fürbas
                                <expan>überhabe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
